    "exceptions": [],
    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Minimum size of searched matches. Larger values increase compression and decompression speed, but decrease ratio. Note that Zstandard can still find matches of smaller size, it just tweaks its search algorithm to look for this size and larger. For all strategies < btopt, the effective minimum is 4; for all strategies > fast, the effective maximum is 6. A value of zero causes the value to be selected automatically."
    },
